  NOTIF --- NOT_F2[✅ Token registration / unregister]:::feat
  NOTIF --- NOT_F3[✅ Notification annulation activité]:::feat
  NOTIF --- NOT_F4[🔜 Notification formation groupe]:::planned
  NOTIF --- NOT_F5[🔜 Notification nouveau message]:::planned
