  %% ============================================================
  %% CONNEXIONS ENTRE DOMAINES
  %% ============================================================
  AUTH ==>|session| PROFILE
  AUTH ==>|push token| NOTIF
  PROFILE ==>|intérêts| ACTIVITIES
  PROFILE ==>|amis| SOCIAL
  ACTIVITIES ==>|créneaux| GROUPS
  ACTIVITIES ==>|inscription| PAYMENT
  ACTIVITIES ==>|présence| CHECKIN
  ACTIVITIES ==>|inviter +1| PLUSONE
  PLUSONE ==>|paiement duo| PAYMENT
  GROUPS ==>|conv. auto| MESSAGING
  SOCIAL ==>|chat privé| MESSAGING
  BUSINESS ==>|host| ACTIVITIES
  BUSINESS ==>|staff| CHECKIN
